Taco Viva Inc said it namedDonald Ryan as president and chief operating officer of thecompany.    He assumes the president's slot formerly held by J. BrionFoulke III, who retains his positions as chairman and chiefexecutive officer, the company said.    Ryan most recenty served as president of &lt;InterimRestaurant Management Inc>, a firm specializing in rejuvenatingoperations of ailing restaurant chains.    Ryan will join Taco Viva in early November, the companysaid. Reuter&#3;